    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept and good overall, this is a nice, honest car that shows well and offers a great balance of condition and value. It presents cleanly inside and out, has the kind of normal light wear you\u2019d expect from a properly used vehicle, and is ready to be enjoyed right away. A strong driver for someone looking for a quality car without paying mint-condition money.",
