    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition that shows it has been cared for over time. It presents nicely inside and out, with normal light wear for its age and use, including minor cosmetic imperfections you\u2019d expect from a good driver-quality example. The interior, paint, and trim are all respectable overall, and a buyer should expect a clean, honest vehicle rather than a perfect show car. A solid choice for someone looking for a good-condition car that\u2019s ready to enjoy and easy to own.",
      "price": 32900.0,
